        "Residential",
        "Commercial",
        "Industrial",
        "sankey-beta"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个能源来源，三个目标用户类型。我想确认一下数据：电力这边住宅50、商业30、工业20，这样分配合理吗？还有天然气和太阳能的具体数值您有吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Electricity",
        "Residential",
        "Commercial",
        "Industrial"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "天然气按住宅40、商业35、工业25来分。太阳能这边住宅占比最高，给60，商业25，工业15。这样能看出住宅是太阳能的主要受益者。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gas",
        "Solar",
        "Residential",
        "Commercial",
        "Industrial"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：电力总计100，天然气总计100，太阳能也是100。三个来源的总量平衡，流向三个目标列。住宅总共拿到150，商业90，工业60。这个结构我清楚了，开始绘制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Electricity",
        "Gas",
        "Solar",
        "Residential",
        "Commercial",
        "Industrial"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
